examples.en: He gave me the keys for safekeeping.
She had put her watch in her pocket for safekeeping.
He confided his money to his brother's safekeeping.
The documents are in the safekeeping of our lawyers.
My friend left her jewelry with me for safekeeping when she went on vacation.
While she was away on business, the single mom entrusted her daughter into her in-laws' safekeeping.
